      "content": "wait what? i'm just trying to do a serious audit here. i dont need metaphors, i just need to know if this is a unit of measure error or maybe a logging lag in the ERP system. \n\ncan you give me a professional breakdown of the actual logistical reasons why these specific numbers might be drifting? like, what are the standard industry causes for small shrinkage in electronics?",
